§ 171.
Germanic þ remained in Gothic, as
þagkjan, OE. þencan, OS. thenkian, OHG. denken, to think;
qiþan, O.Icel. kveða, OE. cweþan, OS. queðan, OHG. quedan, to say;
acc. áiþ, OE. āþ, OS. ēð, OHG. eid, oath;
and similarly
þaírh, through;
